Work faster.

Built to provide a solid ecosystem for professionals and hobbyiest alike, Cavrn it by far the most intuitive way to program AVR Microcontrollers meaning less time spent reading documentation and more is spent actually building.

Be efficient.

When using Cavrn you can gurantee that the code you're using was specially designed for you microcontroller to provide the most efficient performance with the least effort on your part.

Get creative.

Cavrn allows you to take your attention off of the nuances of getting registers set and commuincation up, and brings it back to the heart of whatever you're working on. With Cavrn not only will it be simple but you can gurantee it's faster and more optimally performant than other libraries.
